OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FRaw sewage was dumped into the sea off
OL,7,Fthe Kent coastline for nearly five
OL,8,Fhours due to a computer error at
OL,9,FSouthern Water, a court has heard.
OL,11,FThe water company is due to be
OL,12,Fsentenced today (17th July) at
OL,13,FCanterbury Crown Court after admitting
OL,14,F13 offences last April relating to
OL,15,Fsewage discharges at pumping stations
OL,16,Fbetween 2019 and 2021.
OL,18,FOn one occasion, the court heard that
OL,19,Funtreated sewage was dumped into the
OL,20,Fsea due to a computer control fault at
OL,21,FBroadstairs wastewater station.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
