CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FIn total, nine counts involve
OL,7,Fincidents of untreated sewage dumped
OL,8,Foff the Kent coast while three counts
OL,9,Fwere over failure to notify
OL,10,Fauthorities of the discharges as soon
OL,11,Fas practicable and within 24 hours of
OL,12,Fa warning, a condition of their
OL,13,Fenvironmental permit.
OL,15,FA final conviction was for failing to
OL,16,Fhave a standby pump at Margate's
OL,17,Fstation between July 27 2019 and
OL,18,FOctober 4 2020 in breach of its permit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
