OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard details of the
OL,7,Foffences including an intermittent
OL,8,Fflow of sewage on July 20 2019 at the
OL,9,FMargate site that lasted from around
OL,10,F2am to just before midnight. The
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency was not notified
OL,12,Funtil more than 32 hours after the
OL,13,Ffirst discharge.
OL,15,FProsecutor Andrew Marshall said the
OL,16,Fsewage that came out into the sea at a
OL,17,Fshorter distance from the shore was
OL,18,F"unscreened" ` which means solid waste
OL,19,Fremained in the sewage ` and that
OL,20,Fthere was a lot of sewage debris
OL,21,Fwashed up on the coast.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FWarnings were put in place on the
OL,7,Fbeach between 17th and 19th February
OL,8,Fwhile company-contracted cleaners
OL,9,Fswept the beach for waste.
OL,11,FThe court also heard that sewage
OL,12,Fpollution discharges at Margate and
OL,13,FBroadstairs stations between June 16
OL,14,Fand 17 2021 led to 11 bathing waters
OL,15,Fbeing closed by Thanet council for a
OL,16,Fweek in a "high profile pollution
OL,17,Fincident".
OL,19,FPictures shown to court showed waste
OL,20,Fin the water, closure notices and an
OL,21,Fempty beach with a red flag on display.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
