FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FOn the victim impact of the offences,
OL,7,FMr Marshall said tourism is a "major
OL,8,Findustry" in Thanet with 20% of
OL,9,Femployment related to tourism and
OL,10,Fbeaches and bays being a "primary
OL,11,Fmotivator" for people's visits.
OL,13,FThanet District Council's director of
OL,14,Fenvironment Michael Humber wrote in a
OL,15,Fstatement that the reputational damage
OL,16,Fof any pollution related incident is
OL,17,F"hugely damaging".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,FThe court heard pollution incidents in
OL,7,Fthe summer can be particularly
OL,8,Fdamaging to the local economy when
OL,9,Fbeaches are at their busiest.
OL,11,FMr Humber said 2021 was extremely
OL,12,Fimportant for recovery for the local
OL,13,Feconomy, and the 17 June incident was
OL,14,F"particularly negatively impactful".
OL,16,FDefending Southern Water, barrister
OL,17,FDominic Kay KC said there has been new
OL,18,Fleadership at the company since 2022
OL,19,Fand the business has been rebuilt
OL,20,Faround accountability.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
