PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1784380679
OL,3,CRaw sewage dumped off South coast due
OL,4,Cto 'computer error', court hears
OL,6,F"The company as is today is completely
OL,7,Fdifferent to the company not only it
OL,8,Fwas in 2011 and 2013 and 2016 but also
OL,9,Fto 2021," he said.
OL,11,F"I can assure the court it isn't
OL,12,Fsimply words, there is evidence based
OL,13,Fin these statements."
OL,15,FHe added that #38 million has been
OL,16,Fspent on Margate's station such as on
OL,17,F"cutting-edge technology" to prevent
OL,18,Fthese sorts of incidents reoccurring.
